<body>
<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.1 (STRIPS J1, J5) MACHENGYUAN 5: 166, 171 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.1">[日食,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.2">公之]社,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.3">隰朋與鮑叔牙從.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.4">日既,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.5">公問二大夫:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.6">"日之食也,曷為?"</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.7">鮑叔牙答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.8">"眚變,災."</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.9">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.10">"爲齊[...]【競 1】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-1a.11">[...] 言(愆?)曰多."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.2 (STRIP J5) MACHENGYUAN 5: 171 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a.1">鮑叔牙答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a.2">"害將來,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a.3">將有兵,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a.4">有憂於公身."</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a.5">公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-2a.6">"然則可說歟?"</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.3 (STRIPS J5, J6) MACHENGYUAN 5: 171, 172 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.1">隰朋答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.2">"公身【競5】為亡道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.3">不遷於善</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.4">而說之,可乎哉?"</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.5">公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.6">"甚哉,吾不賴.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.7">二三子不謫怒寡人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-3a.8">至於使日食!"</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.4 (STRIPS J6, J2) MACHENGYUAN 5: 172, 169 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.1">鮑叔牙【競 6】與隰朋曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.2">"群臣之辠也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.3">昔高宗祭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.4">有雉雊於彝前.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.5">詔祖己</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.6">而問焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.7">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-4a.8">"是何也?"</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.5 (STRIPS J2, J7, J4) MACHENGYUAN 5: 169, 173, 170 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.1">祖己答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.2">"昔先君【競 2】格(=告) 王:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.3">“天不見害,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.4">地不生孼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.5">則訴諸鬼神曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.6">天地盟明弃我矣;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.7">近臣不諫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.8">遠者不謗,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-5a.9">則攸[?]諸鄉【競 7】里."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.6 (STRIP J4) MACHENGYUAN 5: 170 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-6a.1">含(今)此祭之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-6a.2">得福者也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-6a.3">請禳之以衰汲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-6a.4">既祭之後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-6a.5">焉修先王之灋."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.7 (STRIPS J4, J3, J8) MACHENGYUAN 5: 170, 169, 174 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.1">高宗命傅說禳之以【競 4】祭.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.2">既祭焉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.3">命行先王之灋.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.4">發故度,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.5">行故作.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.6">廢作者死,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.7">弗行者死.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.8">不出三年,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.9">狄人之附者七百【競 3】邦.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.10">此能從善</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-7a.11">而去過者."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.8 (STRIPS J8, J9) MACHENGYUAN 5: 174, 175 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a.1">公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a.2">"吾不知其為不善也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a.3">今内之不得百姓,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a.4">外之為諸侯笑.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a.5">寡人之不 【競 8】 肖也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-8a.6">豈不二子之憂也哉?"</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.9 (STRIPS J9, J10) MACHENGYUAN 5: 175, 176 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.1">隰朋與鮑叔牙皆拜,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.2">起而言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.3">"公身為亡道;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.4">擁華孟子</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.5">以馳於郳【競 9】廷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.6">驅逐畋弋</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-9a.7">無期度.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.9 (STRIPS J9, J10) MACHENGYUAN 5: 175, 176 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.1">隰朋與鮑叔牙皆拜,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.2">起而言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.3">"公身為亡道;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.4">擁華孟子</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.5">以馳於郳【競 9】廷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.6">驅逐畋弋</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-10a.7">無期度.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.11 (STRIPS B4, B5) MACHENGYUAN 5: 185, 186 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.1">士民獵樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.2">篤愒倍忨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.3">疲弊齊邦.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.4">日成(逞)于縱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.5">弗顧前後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.6">百【鮑 4】姓皆怨恨,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.7">奄然將亡.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.8">公弗詰蠲 [=禁除],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.9">臣雖欲訐</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-11a.10">或不得見.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.12 (STRIPS B5, B6) MACHENGYUAN 5: 186, 187 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.1">公胡弗察:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.2">人之性三,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.3">食, 色, 愒.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.4">今豎刁匹夫</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.5">而欲【鮑 5】知[?] 萬乘之邦</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.6">而潰朘,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.7">其為災也深矣;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.8">易牙人之邪者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.9">而食人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.10">其為不仁厚矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.11">公弗圖,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-12a.12">必害公身."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.13 (STRIPS B6, B7) MACHENGYUAN 5: 187, 188 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.1">公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.2">"然則奚【鮑 6】如?"</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.3">鮑叔牙答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.4">"齊邦至惡死</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.5">而上繆其刑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.6">至欲食</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.7">而上厚其斂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.8">至惡苛</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-13a.9">而上不時使."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.14 (STRIPS B7, B3) MACHENGYUAN 5: 188, 184 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a" ed="tls" n="001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a.1">公乃身命祭有司:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a.2">祭服毋黹,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a.3">【鮑 7】器必蠲潔,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a.4">毋内殘器,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a.5">犧牲,珪璧必全如故,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-14a.6">加之以敬.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.15 (STRIPS B3, B1) MACHENGYUAN 5: 184, 182 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a" ed="tls" n="001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.1">乃命有司書籍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.2">復老弱不刑;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.3">畝纆短,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.4">田纆長,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.5">百量鍾;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.6">命【鮑 3】九月除路,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.7">十月而徒梁成,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-15a.8">一之日(?)而車梁成.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.16 (STRIPS B1, B2) MACHENGYUAN 5: 182, 183 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a" ed="tls" n="001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.1">乃命百有司曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.2">"有夏氏觀其容以使,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.3">及其亡也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.4">皆偽其容.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.5">殷人之所以代之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.6">觀其容,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.7">聽其【鮑 1】言.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.8">凡其所以亡,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.9">偽其容,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-16a.10">偽其言.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.17 (STRIP B2) MACHENGYUAN 5: 183 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a" ed="tls" n="001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.1">周人之所以代之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.2">觀其容,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.3">聽[其]言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.4">考實者使.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.5">凡其所以衰亡,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.6">忘其考實也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.7">二三子勉之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-17a.8">寡人將考實."【鮑 2】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JINGJIANNEIZHI 5.22.18 (STRIP B8) MACHENGYUAN 5: 189 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a" ed="tls" n="001-18a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.1">是歲也晉人伐齊,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.2">既至齊地,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.3">晉邦有亂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.4">師乃歸.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.5">雨平地至膝,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.6">復.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.7">日螟蚱亦不為災,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0051_tls_001-18a.8">虹煇亦不為害.【鮑 8】</seg></p>

